        <h2 class="h-md">White-label SEO tools, <span class="accent">answered.</span></h2>
        <p>Common questions from agencies evaluating white-label SEO tools and resale margins. More? Email <a href="mailto:founder@thestacc.com">founder@thestacc.com</a>.</p>
